<p><strong>B·∫°n ƒë∆∞·ª£c khuy·∫øn kh√≠ch ƒë·ªçc <a href="/2017/03/12/convexity/">B√†i 16</a> tr∆∞·ªõc khi ƒë·ªçc b√†i n√†y. N·ªôi dung trong b√†i vi·∫øt n√†y ch·ªß y·∫øu ƒë∆∞·ª£c d·ªãch t·ª´ Ch∆∞∆°ng 4 c·ªßa cu·ªën <em>Convex Optimization</em> trong ph·∫ßn T√†i li·ªáu tham kh·∫£o.</strong>.</p>

<p>B√†i n√†y c≈©ng c√≥ r·∫•t nhi·ªÅu kh√°i ni·ªám m·ªõi v√† nhi·ªÅu l√Ω thuy·∫øt n√™n c√≥ th·ªÉ kh√¥ng h·∫•p d·∫´n nh∆∞ c√°c b√†i kh√°c. Tuy nhi√™n, t√¥i kh√¥ng th·ªÉ b·ªè qua v√¨ kh√¥ng mu·ªën c√°c b·∫°n ho√†n to√†n m·∫•t ph∆∞∆°ng h∆∞·ªõng khi ƒë·ªçc c√°c b√†i sau.</p>

<p>B·∫°n ƒë·ªçc c√≥ th·ªÉ xem b·∫£n pdf <a href="https://github.com/tiepvupsu/tiepvupsu.github.io/blob/master/assets/latex/book_CVX.pdf">t·∫°i ƒë√¢y</a>.</p>

<p><a name="-gioi-thieu"></a></p>

<h2 id="1-gi·ªõi-thi·ªáu">1. Gi·ªõi thi·ªáu</h2>
<p>T√¥i xin b·∫Øt ƒë·∫ßu b√†i vi·∫øt n√†y b·∫±ng ba b√†i to√°n kh√° g·∫ßn v·ªõi th·ª±c t·∫ø:
<a name="-bai-toan-nha-xuat-ban"></a></p>

<h3 id="11-b√†i-to√°n-nh√†-xu·∫•t-b·∫£n">1.1. B√†i to√°n nh√† xu·∫•t b·∫£n</h3>
<p><a name="bai-toan"></a></p>

<h4 id="b√†i-to√°n">B√†i to√°n</h4>
<p>M·ªôt nh√† xu·∫•n b·∫£n (NXB) nh·∫≠n ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒë∆°n h√†ng 600 b·∫£n c·ªßa cu·ªën ‚ÄúMachine Learning c∆° b·∫£n‚Äù t·ªõi Th√°i B√¨nh v√† 400 b·∫£n t·ªõi H·∫£i Ph√≤ng. NXB ƒë√≥ c√≥ 800 cu·ªën ·ªü kho Nam ƒê·ªãnh v√† 700 cu·ªën ·ªü kho H·∫£i D∆∞∆°ng. Gi√° chuy·ªÉn ph√°t m·ªôt cu·ªën s√°ch t·ª´ Nam ƒê·ªãnh t·ªõi Th√°i B√¨nh l√† 50,000 VND (50k), t·ªõi H·∫£i Ph√≤ng l√† 100k. Gi√° chuy·ªÉn ph√°t m·ªôt cu·ªën t·ª´ H·∫£i D∆∞∆°ng  t·ªõi Th√°i B√¨nh l√† 150k, trong khi t·ªõi H·∫£i Ph√≤ng ch·ªâ l√† 40k. H·ªèi ƒë·ªÉ t·ªën √≠t chi ph√≠ chuy·ªÉn ph√°t nh·∫•t, c√¥ng ty ƒë√≥ n√™n ph√¢n ph·ªëi m·ªói kho chuy·ªÉn bao nhi√™u cu·ªën t·ªõi m·ªói ƒë·ªãa ƒëi·ªÉm?</p>

<p><a name="phan-tich"></a></p>

<h4 id="ph√¢n-t√≠ch">Ph√¢n t√≠ch</h4>
<p>ƒê·ªÉ cho ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n, ta x√¢y d·ª±ng b·∫£ng s·ªë l∆∞·ª£ng chuy·ªÉn s√°ch t·ª´ ngu·ªìn t·ªõi ƒë√≠ch nh∆∞ sau:</p>

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th style="text-align: center">Ngu·ªìn</th>
      <th style="text-align: center">ƒê√≠ch</th>
      <th style="text-align: center">ƒê∆°n gi√° (\(\times\)10k)</th>
      <th style="text-align: center">S·ªë l∆∞·ª£ng</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">Nam ƒê·ªãnh</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">Th√°i B√¨nh</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">5</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">\(x\)</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">Nam ƒê·ªãnh</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">H·∫£i Ph·ªèng</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">10</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">\(y\)</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">H·∫£i D∆∞∆°ng</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">Th√°i B√¨nh</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">15</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">\(z\)</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="text-align: center">H·∫£i D∆∞∆°ng</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">H·∫£i Ph√≤ng</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">4</td>
      <td style="text-align: center">\(t\)</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<p>T·ªïng chi ph√≠ (objective function) s·∫Ω l√† \(f(x, y, z, t) = 5x + 10y + 15z + 4t\). C√°c ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán r√†ng bu·ªôc (constraints) vi·∫øt d∆∞·ªõi d·∫°ng bi·ªÉu th·ª©c to√°n h·ªçc l√†:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Chuy·ªÉn 600 cu·ªën t·ªõi Th√°i B√¨nh: \(x + z = 600\).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Chuy·ªÉn 400 cu·ªën t·ªõi H·∫£i Ph√≤ng: \(y + t = 400\).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>L·∫•y t·ª´ kho Nam ƒê·ªãnh kh√¥ng qu√° 800: \(x + y \leq 800\).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>L·∫•y t·ª´ kho H·∫£i D∆∞∆°ng kh√¥ng qu√° 700: \(z + t \leq 700\).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>\(x, y, z, t\) l√† c√°c s·ªë t·ª± nhi√™n. R√†ng bu·ªôc l√† s·ªë t·ª± nhi√™n s·∫Ω khi·∫øn cho b√†i to√°n r·∫•t kh√≥ gi·∫£i n·∫øu s·ªë l∆∞·ª£ng bi·∫øn l√† r·∫•t l·ªõn. V·ªõi b√†i to√°n n√†y, ta gi·∫£ s·ª≠ r·∫±ng \(x, y, z, t\) l√† c√°c s·ªë th·ª±c d∆∞∆°ng. Khi t√¨m ƒë∆∞·ª£c nghi·ªám, n·∫øu ch√∫ng kh√¥ng ph·∫£i l√† s·ªë t·ª± nhi√™n, ta s·∫Ω l·∫•y c√°c gi√° tr·ªã t·ª± nhi√™n g·∫ßn nh·∫•t.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>V·∫≠y ta c·∫ßn gi·∫£i b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u sau ƒë√¢y:</p>
<hr />

<p><strong>B√†i to√°n NXB:</strong>
\[
\begin{align}
    (x, y, z, t) =&amp; \arg\min_{x, y, z, t} 5x + 10y + 15z + 4t ~~~~ (1)\newline
    \text{subject to:}~ &amp; x + z = 600 ~~~~ (2)\newline
                        &amp; y + t = 400 ~~~~ (3) \newline
                        &amp; x + y \leq 800 ~~~(4) \newline
                        &amp; z + t \leq 700 ~~~ (5)\newline
                        &amp; x, y, z, t \geq 0 ~~~ (6)
\end{align}
\]</p>
<hr />

<p>Nh·∫≠n th·∫•y r·∫±ng h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u (objective function) l√† m·ªôt h√†m tuy·∫øn t√≠nh c·ªßa c√°c bi·∫øn \(x, y, z, t\). C√°c ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán r√†ng bu·ªôc ƒë·ªÅu c√≥ d·∫°ng <em>hyperplanes</em> ho·∫∑c <em>haflspaces</em>, ƒë·ªÅu l√† c√°c r√†ng bu·ªôc tuy·∫øn t√≠nh (linear constraints). B√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u v·ªõi c·∫£ <em>objective function</em> v√† <em>constraints</em> ƒë·ªÅu l√† <em>linear</em> ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† <strong>Linear Programming (LP)</strong>. D·∫°ng t·ªïng qu√°t v√† c√°ch th·ª©c l·∫≠p tr√¨nh ƒë·ªÉ gi·∫£i m·ªôt b√†i to√°n thu·ªôc lo·∫°i n√†y s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c cho trong ph·∫ßn sau c·ªßa b√†i vi·∫øt n√†y.</p>

<p><em>Nghi·ªám cho b√†i to√°n n√†y c√≥ th·ªÉ nh·∫≠n th·∫•y ngay l√† \(x = 600, y = 0, z = 0, t = 400\). N·∫øu r√†ng bu·ªôc nhi·ªÅu h∆°n v√† s·ªë bi·∫øn nhi·ªÅu h∆°n, ch√∫ng ta c·∫ßn m·ªôt l·ªùi gi·∫£i c√≥ th·ªÉ t√≠nh ƒë∆∞·ª£c b·∫±ng c√°ch l·∫≠p tr√¨nh.</em></p>

<p><a name="-bai-toan-canh-tac"></a></p>

<h3 id="12-b√†i-to√°n-canh-t√°c">1.2. B√†i to√°n canh t√°c</h3>
<p><a name="bai-toan-1"></a></p>

<h4 id="b√†i-to√°n-1">B√†i to√°n</h4>
<p>M·ªôt anh n√¥ng d√¢n c√≥ t·ªïng c·ªông 10ha (10 hecta) ƒë·∫•t canh t√°c. Anh d·ª± t√≠nh tr·ªìng c√† ph√™ v√† h·ªì ti√™u tr√™n s·ªë ƒë·∫•t n√†y v·ªõi t·ªïng chi ph√≠ cho vi·ªác tr·ªìng n√†y l√† kh√¥ng qu√° 16T (tri·ªáu ƒë·ªìng). Chi ph√≠ ƒë·ªÉ tr·ªìng c√† ph√™ l√† 2T cho 1ha, ƒë·ªÉ tr·ªìng h·ªì ti√™u l√† 1T/ha/. Th·ªùi gian tr·ªìng c√† ph√™ l√† 1 ng√†y/ha v√† h·ªì ti√™u l√† 4 ng√†y/ha; trong khi anh ch·ªâ c√≥ th·ªùi gian t·ªïng c·ªông l√† 32 ng√†y. Sau khi tr·ª´ t·∫•t c·∫£ c√°c chi ph√≠ (bao g·ªìm chi ph√≠ tr·ªìng c√¢y), m·ªói ha c√† ph√™ mang l·∫°i l·ª£i nhu·∫≠n 5T, m·ªói ha h·ªì ti√™u mang l·∫°i l·ª£i nhu·∫≠n 3T. H·ªèi anh ph·∫£i tr·ªìng nh∆∞ th·∫ø n√†o ƒë·ªÉ t·ªëi ƒëa l·ª£i nhu·∫≠n? (<em>C√°c s·ªë li·ªáu c√≥ th·ªÉ v√¥ l√Ω v√¨ ch√∫ng ƒë√£ ƒë∆∞·ª£c ch·ªçn ƒë·ªÉ b√†i to√°n ra nghi·ªám ƒë·∫πp</em>)</p>

<p><a name="phan-tich-1"></a></p>

<h4 id="ph√¢n-t√≠ch-1">Ph√¢n t√≠ch</h4>
<p>G·ªçi \(x\) v√† \(y\) l·∫ßn l∆∞·ª£t l√† s·ªë ha c√† ph√™ v√† h·ªì ti√™u m√† anh n√¥ng d√¢n n√™n tr·ªìng. L·ª£i nhu·∫≠n anh ·∫•y thu ƒë∆∞·ª£c l√† \(f(x, y) = 5x + 3y\) (tri·ªáu ƒë·ªìng).</p>

<p>C√°c r√†ng bu·ªôc trong b√†i to√°n n√†y l√†:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>T·ªïng di·ªán t√≠ch tr·ªìng kh√¥ng v∆∞·ª£t qu√° 10: \(x + y \leq 10\).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>T·ªïng chi ph√≠ tr·ªìng kh√¥ng v∆∞·ª£t qu√° 16T: \(2x + y \leq 16\).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>T·ªïng th·ªùi gian tr·ªìng kh√¥ng v∆∞·ª£t qu√° 32 ng√†y: \(x + 4y \leq 32\).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Di·ªán t√≠ch c√† ph√™ v√† h·ªì ti√™u l√† c√°c s·ªë kh√¥ng √¢m: \(x, y \geq 0\).</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>V·∫≠y ta c√≥ b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u sau ƒë√¢y:</p>
<hr />

<p><strong>B√†i to√°n canh t√°c:</strong>
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
    (x, y) =&amp; \arg\max_{x, y} 5x + 3y ~~~~ (7)\newline
    \text{subject to:}~ &amp; x + y \leq 10 ~~~~ (8)\newline
                        &amp; 2x + y \leq 16 ~~~(9) \newline
                        &amp; x + 4y \leq 32 ~~~ (10)\newline
                        &amp; x, y \geq 0 ~~~ (11)
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>
<hr />

<p>B√†i to√°n n√†y h∆°i kh√°c m·ªôt ch√∫t l√† ta c·∫ßn <em>t·ªëi ƒëa h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u</em> thay v√¨ t·ªëi thi·ªÉu n√≥. Vi·ªác chuy·ªÉn b√†i to√°n n√†y v·ªÅ b√†i to√°n <em>t·ªëi thi·ªÉu</em> c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c th·ª±c hi·ªán ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n b·∫±ng c√°ch ƒë·ªïi d·∫•u h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u. Khi ƒë√≥ h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u v·∫´n l√† <em>linear</em>, c√°c r√†ng bu·ªôc v·∫´n l√† c√°c <em>linear constraints</em>, ta l·∫°i c√≥ m·ªôt b√†i to√°n <strong>Linear Programming (LP)</strong> n·ªØa.</p>

<p>B·∫°n c≈©ng c√≥ th·ªÉ d·ª±a v√†o h√¨nh minh ho·∫° d∆∞·ªõi ƒë√¢y ƒë·ªÉ suy ra nghi·ªám c·ªßa b√†i to√°n:</p>
<hr />

<div class="imgcap">
 <img src="/assets/17_convexopt/planting.png" align="center" width="400" />
 <div class="thecap">H√¨nh 1. Minh ho·∫° nghi·ªám cho b√†i to√°n canh t√°c.</div>
</div>
<hr />

<p>V√πng m√†u x√°m c√≥ d·∫°ng <em>polyhedron</em> (trong tr∆∞·ªùng h·ª£p n√†y l√† ƒëa gi√°c) ch√≠nh l√† t·∫≠p h·ª£p c√°c ƒëi·ªÉm tho·∫£ m√£n c√°c r√†ng bu·ªôc t·ª´ \(8)\) ƒë·∫øn \((11)\). C√°c ƒë∆∞·ªùng n√©t ƒë·ª©t c√≥ m√†u ch√≠nh l√† c√°c ƒë∆∞·ªùng ƒë·ªìng m·ª©c c·ªßa h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u \(5x + 3y\), m·ªói ƒë∆∞·ªùng ·ª©ng v·ªõi m·ªôt gi√° tr·ªã kh√°c nhau v·ªõi ƒë∆∞·ªùng c√†ng ƒë·ªè ·ª©ng v·ªõi gi√° tr·ªã c√†ng cao. M·ªôt c√°ch tr·ª±c quan, nghi·ªám c·ªßa b√†i to√°n c√≥ th·ªÉ t√¨m ƒë∆∞·ª£c b·∫±ng c√°ch di chuy·ªÉn ƒë∆∞·ªùng n√©t ƒë·ª©t m√†u xanh v·ªÅ ph√≠a b√™n ph·∫£i (ph√≠a l√†m cho gi√° tr·ªã c·ªßa h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u l·ªõn h∆°n) ƒë·∫øn khi n√≥ kh√¥ng c√≤n ƒëi·ªÉm chung v·ªõi ph·∫ßn ƒëa gi√°c m√†u x√°m n·ªØa.</p>

<p>C√≥ th·ªÉ nh·∫≠n th·∫•y nghi·ªám c·ªßa b√†i to√°n ch√≠nh l√† ƒëi·ªÉm m√†u xanh l√† giao ƒëi·ªÉm c·ªßa hai ƒë∆∞·ªùng th·∫≥ng \(x + y = 10\) v√† \(2x + y = 16\). Gi·∫£i h·ªá ph∆∞∆°ng tr√¨nh n√†y ta c√≥ \(x^* = 6\) v√† \(y^* = 4\). T·ª©c anh n√¥ng d√¢n n√™n tr·ªìng 6ha c√† ph√™ v√† 4ha h·ªì ti√™u. L√∫c ƒë√≥ l·ª£i nhu·∫≠n thu ƒë∆∞·ª£c l√† \(5x^* + 3y^* = 42 \) tri·ªáu ƒë·ªìng, trong khi anh ch·ªâ m·∫•t th·ªùi gian l√† 22 ng√†y. (<em>Ch·ªãu t√≠nh to√°n c√°i l√† kh√°c ngay, l√†m √≠t, h∆∞·ªüng nhi·ªÅu</em>).</p>

<p>ƒê√¢y ch√≠nh l√† c√°ch gi·∫£i trong s√°ch to√°n l·ªõp 10 (ng√†y t√¥i h·ªçc l·ªõp 10).</p>

<p>V·ªõi nhi·ªÅu bi·∫øn h∆°n v√† nhi·ªÅu r√†ng bu·ªôc h∆°n, ch√∫ng ta li·ªáu c√≥ th·ªÉ v·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c h√¨nh nh∆∞ th·∫ø n√†y ƒë·ªÉ nh√¨n ra nghi·ªám hay kh√¥ng? C√¢u tr·∫£ l·ªùi c·ªßa t√¥i l√† n√™n t√¨m m·ªôt c√¥ng c·ª• ƒë·ªÉ v·ªõi nhi·ªÅu bi·∫øn h∆°n v√† v·ªõi c√°c r√†ng bu·ªôc kh√°c nhau, ch√∫ng ta c√≥ th·ªÉ t√¨m ra nghi·ªám g·∫ßn nh∆∞ ngay l·∫≠p t·ª©c.
<a name="-bai-toan-dong-thung"></a></p>

<h3 id="13-b√†i-to√°n-ƒë√≥ng-th√πng">1.3. B√†i to√°n ƒë√≥ng th√πng</h3>
<p><a name="bai-toan-2"></a></p>

<h4 id="b√†i-to√°n-2">B√†i to√°n</h4>
<p>M·ªôt c√¥ng ty ph·∫£i chuy·ªÉn 400 \(m^3\) c√°t t·ªõi ƒë·ªãa ƒëi·ªÉm x√¢y d·ª±ng ·ªü b√™n kia s√¥ng b·∫±ng c√°ch thu√™ m·ªôt chi·∫øc x√† lan. Ngo√†i chi ph√≠ v·∫≠n chuy·ªÉn m·ªôt l∆∞·ª£t ƒëi v·ªÅ l√† 100k c·ªßa chi·∫øc x√† lan, c√¥ng ty ƒë√≥ ph·∫£i thi·∫øt k·∫ø m·ªôt th√πng h√¨nh h·ªôp ch·ªØ nh·∫≠t ƒë·∫∑t tr√™n x√† lan ƒë·ªÉ ƒë·ª±ng c√°t. Chi·∫øc th√πng n√†y kh√¥ng c·∫ßn n·∫Øp, chi ph√≠ cho c√°c m·∫∑t xung quanh l√† 1T/\(m^2\), cho m·∫∑t ƒë√°y l√† 2T/\(m^2\). H·ªèi k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc c·ªßa chi·∫øc th√πng ƒë√≥ nh∆∞ th·∫ø n√†o ƒë·ªÉ t·ªïng chi ph√≠ v·∫≠n chuy·ªÉn l√† nh·ªè nh·∫•t. ƒê·ªÉ cho ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n, gi·∫£ s·ª≠ c√°t ch·ªâ ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒë·ªï ngang ho·∫∑c th·∫•p h∆°n v·ªõi ph·∫ßn tr√™n c·ªßa th√†nh th√πng, kh√¥ng c√≥ ng·ªçn. Gi·∫£ s·ª≠ th√™m r·∫±ng x√† lan <em>r·ªông v√¥ h·∫°n</em> v√† ch·ª©a ƒë∆∞·ª£c s·ª©c n·∫∑ng v√¥ h·∫°n, gi·∫£ s·ª≠ n√†y khi·∫øn b√†i to√°n d·ªÖ gi·∫£i h∆°n.</p>

<p><a name="phan-tich-2"></a></p>

<h4 id="ph√¢n-t√≠ch-2">Ph√¢n t√≠ch</h4>
<p>Gi·∫£ s·ª≠ chi·∫øc th√πng c·∫ßn l√†m c√≥ chi·ªÅu d√†i l√† \(x\) (\(m\)), chi·ªÅu r·ªông l√† \(y\) v√† chi·ªÅu cao l√† \(z\). Th·ªÉ t√≠ch c·ªßa th√πng l√† \(xyz\) (ƒë∆°n v·ªã l√† \(m^3\)). C√≥ hai lo·∫°i chi ph√≠ l√†:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p><em>Chi ph√≠ thu√™ x√† lan:</em> s·ªë chuy·∫øn x√† lan ph·∫£i thu√™ l√† \(\frac{400}{xyz}\) (ta h√£y t·∫°m gi·∫£ s·ª≠ r·∫±ng ƒë√¢y l√† m·ªôt s·ªë t·ª± nhi√™n, vi·ªác l√†m tr√≤n n√†y s·∫Ω kh√¥ng thay ƒë·ªïi k·∫øt qu·∫£ ƒë√°ng k·ªÉ v√¨ chi ph√≠ v·∫≠n chuy·ªÉn m·ªôt chuy·∫øn l√† nh·ªè so v·ªõi chi ph√≠ l√†m th√πng). S·ªë ti·ªÅn ph·∫£i tr·∫£ cho x√† lan s·∫Ω l√† \(0.1\frac{400}{xyz} = \frac{40}{xyz}\).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><em>Chi ph√≠ l√†m th√πng:</em> Di·ªán t√≠ch xung quanh c·ªßa th√πng l√† \(2 (x + y)z \). Di·ªán t√≠ch ƒë√°y l√† \(xy\). V·∫≠y t·ªïng chi ph√≠ l√†m th√πng l√† \(2(x +y)z + 2xy = 2(xy + yz + zx)\).</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>T·ªïng to√†n b·ªô chi ph√≠ l√† \(f(x, y, z) = 40x^{-1}y^{-1}z^{-1} + 2(xy + yz + zx)\). ƒêi·ªÅu ki·ªán r√†ng bu·ªôc duy nh·∫•t l√† k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc th√πng ph·∫£i l√† c√°c s·ªë d∆∞∆°ng. V·∫≠y ta c√≥ b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u sau:</p>
<hr />

<p><strong>B√†i to√°n v·∫≠n chuy·ªÉn:</strong>
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
    (x, y) =&amp; \arg\min_{x, y, z} 40x^{-1}y^{-1}z^{-1} + 2(xy + yz + zx) ~~~~ (13)\newline
    \text{subject to:}~ &amp; x, y, z &gt; 0 ~~~~ (14)\newline
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>
<hr />

<p>B√†i to√°n n√†y thu·ªôc lo·∫°i <strong>Geometric Programming (GP)</strong>. ƒê·ªãnh nghƒ©a c·ªßa GP v√† c√°ch d√πng c√¥ng c·ª• t·ªëi ∆∞u s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c tr√¨nh b√†y trong ph·∫ßn sau c·ªßa b√†i vi·∫øt.</p>

<p><em>Nh·∫≠n th·∫•y r·∫±ng b√†i n√†y ho√†n to√†n c√≥ th·ªÉ d√πng b·∫•t ƒë·∫≥ng th·ª©c Cauchy ƒë·ªÉ gi·∫£i ƒë∆∞·ª£c, nh∆∞ng t√¥i v·∫´n mu·ªën m·ªôt l·ªùi gi·∫£i cho b√†i to√°n t·ªïng qu√°t sao cho c√≥ th·ªÉ l·∫≠p tr√¨nh ƒë∆∞·ª£c.</em></p>

<p>(L·ªùi gi·∫£i:
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
    f(x, y, z) &amp;=&amp; \frac{20}{xyz} + \frac{20}{xyz} + 2xy + 2yz + 2zx \newline
               &amp;\geq &amp; 5\sqrt[5]{3200}
\end{eqnarray}
\]
d·∫•u b·∫±ng x·∫£y ra khi v√† ch·ªâ khi \(x = y = z = \sqrt[5]{10}\). B√†i n√†y c√≥ l·∫Ω h·ª£p v·ªõi c√°c k·ª≥ thi v√¨ d·ªØ ki·ªán qu√° ƒë·∫πp. C√° nh√¢n t√¥i th√≠ch c√°c ƒë·ªÅ b√†i ra ki·ªÉu n√†y h∆°n l√† y√™u c·∫ßu ƒëi t√¨m gi√° tr·ªã nh·ªè nh·∫•t c·ªßa m·ªôt bi·ªÉu th·ª©c nh√†m ch√°n, nhi·ªÅu h·ªçc sinh cho r·∫±ng kh√¥ng bi·∫øt h·ªçc b·∫•t ƒë·∫≥ng th·ª©c ƒë·ªÉ l√†m g√¨!)
<!-- http://www.pitt.edu/~jrclass/opt/notes6.pdf --></p>

<p>N·∫øu c√≥ c√°c r√†ng bu·ªôc v·ªÅ k√≠ch th∆∞·ªõc c·ªßa th√πng v√† tr·ªçng l∆∞·ª£ng m√† x√† lan t·∫£i ƒë∆∞·ª£c th√¨ c√≥ th·ªÉ t√¨m ƒë∆∞·ª£c l·ªùi gi·∫£i ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n nh∆∞ th·∫ø n√†y kh√¥ng?</p>

<p>Nh·ªØng b√†i to√°n tr√™n ƒë√¢y ƒë·ªÅu l√† c√°c b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u. Ch√≠nh x√°c h∆°n n·ªØa, ch√∫ng ƒë·ªÅu l√† c√°c b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u l·ªìi (<em>convex optimization problems</em>) nh∆∞ c√°c b·∫°n s·∫Ω th·∫•y ·ªü ph·∫ßn sau. V√† vi·ªác t√¨m l·ªùi gi·∫£i c√≥ th·ªÉ kh√¥ng m·∫•y kh√≥ khƒÉn, th·∫≠m ch√≠ gi·∫£i b·∫±ng tay c≈©ng c√≥ th·ªÉ ra k·∫øt qu·∫£. Tuy nhi√™n, m·ª•c ƒë√≠ch c·ªßa b√†i vi·∫øt n√†y kh√¥ng ph·∫£i l√† h∆∞·ªõng d·∫´n c√°c b·∫°n gi·∫£i c√°c b√†i to√°n tr√™n <em>b·∫±ng tay</em>, m√† l√† c√°ch nh·∫≠n di·ªán c√°c b√†i to√°n v√† ƒë∆∞a ch√∫ng v·ªÅ c√°c d·∫°ng m√† c√°c toolboxes s·∫µn c√≥ c√≥ th·ªÉ gi√∫p ch√∫ng ta. Tr√™n th·ª±c t·∫ø, l∆∞·ª£ng d·ªØ ki·ªán v√† s·ªë bi·∫øn c·∫ßn t·ªëi ∆∞u l·ªõn h∆°n nhi·ªÅu, ch√∫ng ta kh√¥ng th·ªÉ gi·∫£i c√°c b√†i to√°n tr√™n <em>b·∫±ng tay</em> ƒë∆∞·ª£c.</p>

<p>Tr∆∞·ªõc h·∫øt, ch√∫ng ta c·∫ßn hi·ªÉu c√°c kh√°i ni·ªám v·ªÅ <em>convex optimization problems</em> v√† t·∫°i sao <em>convex</em> l·∫°i quan tr·ªçng. (B·∫°n ƒë·ªçc c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë·ªçc t·ªõi <a href="/2017/03/19/convexopt/#-linear-programming">ph·∫ßn 4</a> n·∫øu kh√¥ng mu·ªën bi·∫øt c√°c kh√°i ni·ªám v√† ƒë·ªãnh l√Ω to√°n  trong ph·∫ßn 2 v√† 3.)</p>

<p><a name="-nhac-lai-bai-toan-toi-uu"></a></p>

<h2 id="2-nh·∫Øc-l·∫°i-b√†i-to√°n-t·ªëi-∆∞u">2. Nh·∫Øc l·∫°i b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u</h2>
<p><a name="-cac-khai-niem-co-ban"></a></p>

<h3 id="21-c√°c-kh√°i-ni·ªám-c∆°-b·∫£n">2.1. C√°c kh√°i ni·ªám c∆° b·∫£n</h3>
<p>T√¥i xin nh·∫Øc l·∫°i b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u ·ªü d·∫°ng t·ªïng qu√°t:
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
\mathbf{x}^* &amp;=&amp; \arg\min_{\mathbf{x}} f_0(\mathbf{x}) \newline
\text{subject to:}~ &amp;&amp; f_i(\mathbf{x}) \leq 0, ~~ i = 1, 2, \dots, m ~~~(15)\newline
&amp;&amp; h_j(\mathbf{x}) = 0, ~~ j = 1, 2, \dots, p
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>

<p>Ph√°t bi·ªÉu b·∫±ng l·ªùi: T√¨m gi√° tr·ªã c·ªßa bi·∫øn \(\mathbf{x}\) ƒë·ªÉ t·ªëi thi·ªÉu h√†m \(f_0(\mathbf{x})\) trong s·ªë c√°c gi√° tr·ªã c·ªßa \(\mathbf{x}\) tho·∫£ m√£n c√°c ƒëi·ªáu hi·ªán r√†ng bu·ªôc. Ta c√≥ b·∫£ng c√°c t√™n g·ªçi ti·∫øng Anh v√† ti·∫øng Vi·ªát nh∆∞ sau:</p>

<hr />

<table>
  <thead>
    <tr>
      <th>K√Ω hi·ªáu</th>
      <th>Ti·∫øng Anh</th>
      <th>Ti·∫øng Vi·ªát</th>
    </tr>
  </thead>
  <tbody>
    <tr>
      <td>\(\mathbf{x} \in \mathbb{R}^n\)</td>
      <td>optimization variable</td>
      <td>bi·∫øn t·ªëi ∆∞u</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>\(f_0: \mathbb{R}^n \rightarrow \mathbb{R}\)</td>
      <td>objective/los/cost function</td>
      <td>h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>\(f_i(\mathbf{x}) \leq 0 \)</td>
      <td>inequality constraints</td>
      <td>b·∫•t ƒë·∫≥ng th·ª©c r√†ng bu·ªôc</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>\(f_i: \mathbb{R}^n \rightarrow \mathbb{R}\)</td>
      <td>inequality constraint functions</td>
      <td>-</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>\(h_j(\mathbf{x}) = 0 \)</td>
      <td>equality constraints</td>
      <td>ƒë·∫≥ng th·ª©c r√†ng bu·ªôc</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>\(h_j: \mathbb{R}^n \rightarrow \mathbb{R}\)</td>
      <td>equality constraint functions</td>
      <td>-</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td>\(\mathcal{D} = \bigcap_{i=0}^m \text{dom}f_i \cap \bigcap_{pj=1}^p \text{dom}h_i \)</td>
      <td>domain</td>
      <td>t·∫≠p x√°c ƒë·ªãnh</td>
    </tr>
  </tbody>
</table>

<hr />

<p>Ngo√†i ra:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>Khi \(m = p = 0\), b√†i to√°n \((15)\) ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† <em>unconstrained optimization problem</em> (b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u kh√¥ng r√†ng bu·ªôc).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>\(\mathcal{D}\) ch·ªâ l√† t·∫≠p x√°c ƒë·ªãnh, t·ª©c giao c·ªßa t·∫•t c·∫£ c√°c t·∫≠p x√°c ƒë·ªãnh c·ªßa m·ªçi h√†m s·ªë xu·∫•t hi·ªán trong b√†i to√°n. T·∫≠p h·ª£p c√°c ƒëi·ªÉm tho·∫£ m√£n m·ªçi ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán r√†ng bu·ªôc, th√¥ng th∆∞·ªùng, l√† m·ªôt t·∫≠p con c·ªßa \(\mathcal{D}\) ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† <em>feasible set</em> ho·∫∑c <em>constraint set</em>. Khi <em>feasible set</em> l√† m·ªôt t·∫≠p r·ªóng th√¨ ta n√≥i b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u \((15)\) l√† <em>infeasible</em>. N·∫øu m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm n·∫±m trong <em>feasible set</em>, ta g·ªçi ƒëi·ªÉm ƒë√≥ l√† <em>feasible</em>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p><em>Optimal value</em> (<em>gi√° tr·ªã t·ªëi ∆∞u</em>) c·ªßa b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u \((15)\) ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a l√†:
\[
p^* = \text{inf}\{f_0(\mathbf{x}) | f_i(\mathbf{x}) \leq 0, i = 1, \dots, m; h_j(\mathbf{x}) = 0, j = 1, \dots, p\}
\]
trong ƒë√≥ \(\text{inf}\) l√† vi·∫øt t·∫Øt c·ªßa h√†m <a href="http://mathworld.wolfram.com/Infimum.html">infimum</a>. \(p^*\) c√≥ th·ªÉ nh·∫≠n c√°c gi√° tr·ªã \(\pm \infty\). N·∫øu b√†i to√°n l√† <em>infeasible</em>, ta coi \(p^* = + \infty\), N·∫øu h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u kh√¥ng b·ªã ch·∫∑n d∆∞·ªõi (<em>unbounded below</em>) trong t·∫≠p x√°c ƒë·ªãnh, ta coi \(p^* = - \infty\).</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><a name="-optimal-and-locally-optimal-points"></a></p>

<h3 id="22-optimal-and-locally-optimal-points">2.2. Optimal and locally optimal points</h3>
<!-- _M·ªôt v√†i kh√°i ni·ªám trong n√†y c√°c b·∫°n c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë√£ g·∫∑p trong ch∆∞∆°ng tr√¨nh to√°n c·∫•p ba ·ªü Vi·ªát Nam_. -->

<p>M·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm \(\mathbf{x}^*\) ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm <em>optimal point</em> (<em>ƒëi·ªÉm t·ªëi ∆∞u</em>), ho·∫∑c l√† <em>nghi·ªám</em> c·ªßa b√†i to√°n \((15)\) n·∫øu \(\mathbf{x}^*\) l√† <em>feasible</em> v√† \(f_0(\mathbf{x}^*) = p^*\). T·∫•t h·ª£p t·∫•t c·∫£ c√°c <em>optimal points</em> ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† <em>optimal set</em>.</p>

<p>N·∫øu <em>optimal set</em> l√† m·ªôt t·∫≠p <em>kh√¥ng</em> r·ªóng, ta n√≥i b√†i to√°n \((15)\) l√† <em>solvable</em> (<em>gi·∫£i ƒë∆∞·ª£c</em>). Ng∆∞·ª£c l·∫°i, n·∫øu <em>optimal set</em> l√† m·ªôt t·∫≠p r·ªóng, ta n√≥i <em>optimal value</em> l√† <em>kh√¥ng th·ªÉ ƒë·∫°t ƒë∆∞·ª£c</em> (<em>not attained/ not achieved</em>).</p>

<p>V√≠ d·ª•: x√©t h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u \(f(x) = 1/x\) v·ªõi r√†ng bu·ªôc \(x &gt; 0\). <em>Optimal value</em> c·ªßa b√†i to√°n n√†y l√† \(p^* = 0\) nh∆∞ng <em>optimal set</em> l√† m·ªôt t·∫≠p r·ªóng v√¨ kh√¥ng c√≥ gi√° tr·ªã n√†o c·ªßa \(x\) ƒë·ªÉ h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u ƒë·∫°t gi√° tr·ªã 0. L√∫c n√†y ta n√≥i <em>gi√° tr·ªã t·ªëi ∆∞u</em> l√† <em>kh√¥ng ƒë·∫°t ƒë∆∞·ª£c</em>.</p>

<p>V·ªõi h√†m m·ªôt bi·∫øn, m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm l√† <em>c·ª±c ti·ªÉu</em> c·ªßa m·ªôt h√†m s·ªë n·∫øu t·∫°i ƒë√≥, h√†m s·ªë ƒë·∫°t gi√° tr·ªã nh·ªè nh·∫•t trong m·ªôt l√¢n c·∫≠n (v√† l√¢n c·∫≠n n√†y thu·ªôc t·∫≠p x√°c ƒë·ªãnh c·ªßa h√†m s·ªë). Trong kh√¥ng gian 1 chi·ªÅu, <em>l√¢n c·∫≠n</em> ƒë∆∞·ª£c hi·ªÉu l√† tr·ªã tuy·ªát t·ªëi c·ªßa hi·ªáu 2 ƒëi·ªÉm nh·ªè h∆°n m·ªôt gi√° tr·ªã n√†o ƒë√≥.</p>

<p>Trong to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u (th∆∞·ªùng l√† kh√¥ng gian nhi·ªÅu chi·ªÅu), ta g·ªçi m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm \(\mathbf{x}\) l√† <strong>locally optimal</strong> (c·ª±c ti·ªÉu) n·∫øu t·ªìn t·∫°i m·ªôt gi√° tr·ªã (th∆∞·ªùng ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† b√°n kinh) \(R\) sao cho:
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
    f_0(\mathbf{x}) = &amp;\text{inf}\{f_0(\mathbf{z}) | f_i(\mathbf{z}) \leq 0, i = 1, \dots, m, \newline
                 &amp; h_j(\mathbf{z}) = 0, j = 1, \dots, p, ||\mathbf{z} - \mathbf{x}||_2 \leq R\}
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>

<p>N·∫øu m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm <em>feasible</em> \(\mathbf{x}\) tho·∫£ m√£n \(f_i(\mathbf{x}) = 0\), ta n√≥i r·∫±ng b·∫•t ƒë·∫≥ng th·ª©c r√†ng bu·ªôc th·ª© \(i: f_i(\mathbf{x}) = 0\) l√† <em>active</em>. N·∫øu \(f_i(\mathbf{x}) &lt; 0\), ta n√≥i r·∫±ng r√†ng bu·ªôc n√†y l√† <em>inactive</em> t·∫°i \(\mathbf{x}\).</p>

<p><a name="-mot-vai-luu-y"></a></p>

<h3 id="23-m·ªôt-v√†i-l∆∞u-√Ω">2.3. M·ªôt v√†i l∆∞u √Ω</h3>
<p>M·∫∑c d√π trong ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u \((15)\) l√† cho b√†i to√°n <em>t·ªëi thi·ªÉu h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u</em> v·ªõi c√°c r√†ng bu·ªôc tho·∫£ m√£n c√°c ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán nh·ªè h∆°n ho·∫∑c b·∫±ng 0, c√°c b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u v·ªõi <em>t·ªëi ƒëa h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u</em> v√† ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán r√†ng bu·ªôc ·ªü d·∫°ng kh√°c ƒë·ªÅu c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞a v·ªÅ ƒë∆∞·ª£c d·∫°ng n√†y:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>\(\max f_0(\mathbf{x}) \Leftrightarrow\min -f_0(\mathbf{x}) \).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>\(f_i(\mathbf{x}) \leq g(\mathbf{x}) \Leftrightarrow\ f_i(\mathbf{x}) - g(\mathbf{x}) \leq 0\).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>\(f_i(\mathbf{x}) \geq 0 \Leftrightarrow\ -f_i(\mathbf{x}) \leq 0 \).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>\(a \leq f_i(\mathbf{x}) \leq b \Leftrightarrow\ f_i(\mathbf{x}) -b \leq 0\) v√† \(a - f_i(\mathbf{x}) \leq 0\).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>\(f_i(\mathbf{x}) \leq 0 \Leftrightarrow f_i(\mathbf{x}) + s_i = 0 \) v√† \(s_i \geq 0\). \(s_i\) ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† <em>slack variable</em>. Ph√©p bi·∫øn ƒë·ªïi ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n n√†y trong nhi·ªÅu tr∆∞·ªùng h·ª£p l·∫°i t·ªè ra hi·ªáu qu·∫£ v√¨ b·∫•t ƒë·∫≥ng th·ª©c \(s_i \geq 0\) th∆∞·ªùng d·ªÖ gi·∫£i quy·∫øt h∆°n l√† \(f_i(\mathbf{x}) \leq 0\).</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><a name="-bai-toan-toi-uu-loi"></a></p>

<h2 id="3-b√†i-to√°n-t·ªëi-∆∞u-l·ªìi">3. B√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u l·ªìi</h2>

<p>Trong to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u, ch√∫ng ta ƒë·∫∑c bi·ªát quan t√¢m t·ªõi nh·ªØng b√†i to√°n m√† h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u l√† m·ªôt h√†m l·ªìi, v√† <em>feasible set</em> c≈©ng l√† m·ªôt t·∫≠p l·ªìi.
<a name="-dinh-nghia"></a></p>

<h3 id="31-ƒë·ªãnh-nghƒ©a">3.1. ƒê·ªãnh nghƒ©a</h3>
<p>M·ªôt <em>b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u l·ªìi</em> (<em>convex optimization problem</em>) l√† m·ªôt b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u c√≥ d·∫°ng:
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
\mathbf{x}^* &amp;=&amp; \arg\min_{\mathbf{x}} f_0(\mathbf{x}) \newline
\text{subject to:}~ &amp;&amp; f_i(\mathbf{x}) \leq 0, ~~ i = 1, 2, \dots, m ~~~(16)\newline
&amp;&amp; \mathbf{a}_j^T\mathbf{x} - b_j = 0, j = 1, \dots,
\end{eqnarray}
\]
trong ƒë√≥ \(f_0, f_1, \dots, f_m\) l√† c√°c h√†m l·ªìi.</p>

<p>So v·ªõi b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u \((15)\), b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u l·ªìi \((16)\) c√≥ th√™m ba ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán n·ªØa:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p><em>H√†m m·ª•c ti√™u</em> l√† m·ªôt <em>h√†m l·ªìi</em>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>C√°c h√†m b·∫•t ƒë·∫≥ng th·ª©c r√†ng bu·ªôc \(f_i\) l√† c√°c h√†m l·ªìi.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>H√†m ƒë·∫≥ng th·ª©c r√†ng bu·ªôc \(h_j\) l√† <em>affine</em> (h√†m <em>linear</em> c·ªông v·ªõi m·ªôt h·∫≥ng s·ªë n·ªØa ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† <em>affine</em>).</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>M·ªôt v√†i nh·∫≠n x√©t:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>T·∫≠p h·ª£p c√°c ƒëi·ªÉm tho·∫£ m√£n \(h_j(\mathbf{x}) = 0\) l√† m·ªôt t·∫≠p l·ªìi v√¨ n√≥ c√≥ d·∫°ng m·ªôt <em>hyperplane</em>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Khi \(f_i\) l√† m·ªôt <em>h√†m l·ªìi</em> th√¨ t·∫≠p h·ª£p c√°c ƒëi·ªÉm tho·∫£ m√£n \(f_i(\mathbf{x}) \leq 0 \) ch√≠nh l√† <a href="/2017/03/12/convexity/#-\\\alpha-\\-sublevel-sets">0-sublevel set c·ªßa \(f_i\) v√† l√† m·ªôt t·∫≠p l·ªìi</a>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Nh∆∞ v·∫≠y t·∫≠p h·ª£p c√°c ƒëi·ªÉm tho·∫£ m√£n m·ªçi ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán r√†ng bu·ªôc ch√≠nh l√† <a href="/2017/03/12/convexity/#-giao-cua-cac-tap-loi-la-mot-tap-loi">giao ƒëi·ªÉm c·ªßa c√°c <em>t·∫≠p l·ªìi</em>, v√¨ v·∫≠y n√≥ l√† m·ªôt <em>t·∫≠p l·ªìi</em></a>.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><strong>V·∫≠y, trong m·ªôt b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u l·ªìi, ta <em>t·ªëi thi·ªÉu m·ªôt h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u l·ªìi</em> tr√™n m·ªôt <em>t·∫≠p l·ªìi</em></strong>.</p>

<p><a name="-cuc-tieu-cua-bai-toan-toi-uu-loi-chinh-la-diem-toi-uu"></a></p>

<h3 id="32-c·ª±c-ti·ªÉu-c·ªßa-b√†i-to√°n-t·ªëi-∆∞u-l·ªìi-ch√≠nh-l√†-ƒëi·ªÉm-t·ªëi-∆∞u">3.2. C·ª±c ti·ªÉu c·ªßa b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u l·ªìi ch√≠nh l√† ƒëi·ªÉm t·ªëi ∆∞u.</h3>
<p>T√çnh ch·∫•t quan tr·ªçng nh·∫•t c·ªßa b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u l·ªìi ch√≠nh l√† b·∫•t k·ª≥ <em>locally optimal point</em> ch√≠nh l√† m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm <em>(globally) optimal point</em>.</p>

<p>T√≠nh ch·∫•t quan tr·ªçng n√†y c√≥ th·ªÉ ch·ª©ng minh b·∫±ng ph·∫£n ch·ª©ng nh∆∞ sau. G·ªçi  \(\mathbf{x}_0\) l√† m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm <em>locally optimal</em>, t·ª©c:</p>

<p>\[
f_0(\mathbf{x}_0) = \text{inf} \{f_0(\mathbf{x}) | \mathbf{x} ~\text{is feasible}, ||\mathbf{x} - \mathbf{x}_0||_2 \leq R\}
\]</p>

<p>v·ªõi \(R &gt; 0\) n√†o ƒë√≥. Gi·∫£ s·ª≠ \(\mathbf{x}_0\) kh√¥ng ph·∫£i l√† <em>globally optimal point</em>, t·ª©c t·ªìn t·∫°i m·ªôt <em>feasible point</em> \(\mathbf{y}\) sao cho \(f(\mathbf{y}) &lt; f(\mathbf{x}_0)\) (hi·ªÉn nhi√™n r·∫±ng \(\mathbf{y}\) kh√¥ng n·∫±m trong l√¢n c·∫≠n ƒëang x√©t). Ta c√≥ th·ªÉ t√¨m ƒë∆∞·ª£c \(\theta \in [0, 1]\) ƒë·ªß nh·ªè sao cho \(\mathbf{z} = (1 - \theta)\mathbf{x}_0 + \theta\mathbf{y}\) n·∫±m trong l√¢n c·∫≠n c·ªßa \(\mathbf{x}_0\), t·ª©c \(||\mathbf{z} - \mathbf{x}_0||_2 &lt; R\). Ch√∫ √Ω r·∫±ng \(\mathbf{z}\) c≈©ng l√† m·ªôt <em>feasible point</em> v√¨ <em>feasible set</em> l√† m·ªôt <em>t·∫≠p l·ªìi</em>. H∆°n n·ªØa, v√¨ <em>h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u</em> \(f_0\) l√† m·ªôt h√†m l·ªìi, ta c√≥:</p>

<p>\[
\begin{eqnarray}
    f_0(\mathbf{z}) &amp;=&amp; f_0((1 - \theta)\mathbf{x}_0 + \theta \mathbf{y})  \<br />
                    &amp;\leq&amp; (1 - \theta)f_0(\mathbf{x}_0) + \theta f_0(\mathbf{y})\<br />
                    &amp; &lt; &amp; (1 - \theta)f_0(\mathbf{x}_0) + \theta f_0(\mathbf{x}_0) \<br />
                    &amp;=&amp; f_0(\mathbf{x}_0)
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>

<p>ƒëi·ªÅu n√†y m√¢u thu·∫´n v·ªõi gi·∫£ thi·∫øt \(\mathbf{x}_0\) l√† m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm c·ª±c ti·ªÉu. V·∫≠y gi·∫£ s·ª≠ sai, t·ª©c \(\mathbf{x}_0\) ch√≠nh l√† <em>globally optimal point</em> v√† ta c√≥ ƒëi·ªÅu ph·∫£i ch·ª©ng minh.</p>

<p>Ch·ª©ng minh b·∫±ng l·ªùi: gi·∫£ s·ª≠ m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm c·ª±c ti·ªÉu kh√¥ng ph·∫£i l√† ƒëi·ªÉm l√†m cho h√†m s·ªë ƒë·∫°t gi√° tr·ªã nh·ªè nh·∫•t. V·ªõi ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán <em>feasible set</em> v√† <em>h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u</em> l√† l·ªìi, ta lu√¥n t√¨m ƒë∆∞·ª£c m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm kh√°c trong l√¢n c·∫≠n c·ªßa ƒëi·ªÉm c·ª±c ti·ªÉu ƒë√≥ sao cho gi√° tr·ªã c·ªßa h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u t·∫°i ƒëi·ªÉm m·ªõi n√†y nh·ªè h∆°n gi√° tr·ªã c·ªßa h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u t·∫°i ƒëi·ªÉm c·ª±c ti·ªÉu. S·ª± m√¢u thu·∫´n n√†y ch·ªâ ra r·∫±ng v·ªõi m·ªôt b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u l·ªìi, ƒëi·ªÉm c·ª±c ti·ªÉu ph·∫£i l√† ƒëi·ªÉm l√†m cho h√†m s·ªë ƒë·∫°t gi√° tr·ªã nh·ªè nh·∫•t.</p>

<p><a name="-dieu-kien-toi-uu-cho-ham-muc-tieu-kha-vi"></a></p>

<h3 id="33-ƒëi·ªÅu-ki·ªán-t·ªëi-∆∞u-cho-h√†m-m·ª•c-ti√™u-kh·∫£-vi">3.3. ƒêi·ªÅu ki·ªán t·ªëi ∆∞u cho h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u kh·∫£ vi</h3>

<p>N·∫øu h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u \(f_0\) l√† kh·∫£ vi (differentiable), theo <a href="/2017/03/12/convexity/#-first-order-condition">first-order condition</a>, v·ªõi m·ªçi \(\mathbf{x}, \mathbf{y} \in \text{dom}f_0\), ta c√≥:
\[
f_0(\mathbf{x}) \geq f_0(\mathbf{x}_0) + \nabla f_0(\mathbf{x}_0)^T (\mathbf{x} - \mathbf{x}_0)~~~(17)
\]</p>

<p>ƒê·∫∑t \(\mathcal{X}\) l√† <em>feasible set</em>. <strong>ƒêi·ªÅu ki·ªán c·∫ßn v√† ƒë·ªß</strong> ƒë·ªÉ m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm \(\mathbf{x}_0 \in \mathcal{X}\) l√† <em>optimal point</em> l√†:
\[
\nabla f_0(\mathbf{x}_0)^T(\mathbf{x} - \mathbf{x}_0) \geq 0, ~\forall \mathbf{x} \in \mathcal{X} ~~~(18)
\]
T√¥i xin ƒë∆∞·ª£c b·ªè qua vi·ªác ch·ª©ng minh ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán c·∫ßn v√† ƒë·ªß n√†y, b·∫°n ƒë·ªçc c√≥ th·ªÉ t√¨m trong trang 139-140 c·ªßa cu·ªën Convex Optimization trong T√†i li·ªáu tham kh·∫£o.</p>

<p>Xem h√¨nh v·∫Ω d∆∞·ªõi ƒë√¢y:</p>
<hr />

<div class="imgcap">
 <img src="/assets/17_convexopt/optimalitycondition.png" align="center" width="600" />
 <div class="thecap">H√¨nh 2. Bi·ªÉu di·ªÖn h√¨nh h·ªçc c·ªßa ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán t·ªëi ∆∞u cho h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u kh·∫£ vi. C√°c ƒë∆∞·ªùng n√©t ƒë·ª©t c√≥ m√†u t∆∞∆°ng ·ª©ng v·ªõi c√°c level sets (ƒë∆∞·ªùng ƒë·ªìng m·ª©c).</div>
</div>
<hr />

<p>M·ªôt c√°ch h√¨nh h·ªçc, ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán n√†y n√≥i r·∫±ng: N·∫øu \(\mathbf{x}_0\) l√† ƒëi·ªÉm <em>optimal</em> th√¨ v·ªõi m·ªçi \(\mathbf{x} \in \mathcal{X}\), vector ƒëi t·ª´ \(\mathbf{x}_0\) t·ªõi \(\mathbf{x}\) h·ª£p v·ªõi vector \(-\nabla f_0 (\mathbf{x}_0)\) m·ªôt g√≥c t√π. N√≥i c√°ch kh√°c, n·∫øu ta v·∫Ω <em>m·∫∑t ti·∫øp tuy·∫øn</em> c·ªßa h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u t·∫°i \(\mathbf{x}_0\) th√¨ m·ªçi ƒëi·ªÉm <em>feasible</em> n·∫±m v·ªÅ m·ªôt ph√≠a so v·ªõi <em>m·∫∑t ti·∫øp tuy·∫øn n√†y</em>. H∆°n n·ªØa, <em>feasible set</em> n·∫±m v·ªÅ ph√≠a l√†m cho h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u ƒë·∫°t gi√° tr·ªã cao h∆°n \(f_0(\mathbf{x}_0)\). M·∫∑t ti·∫øp tuy·∫øn n√†y ch√≠nh l√† <em>supporting hyperplane</em> c·ªßa <em>feasible set</em> t·∫°i ƒëi·ªÉm \(\mathbf{x}_0\). Nh·∫Øc l·∫°i r·∫±ng khi v·∫Ω c√°c <em>level set</em>, t√¥i th∆∞·ªùng d√πng m√†u lam ƒë·ªÉ ch·ªâ gi√° tr·ªã nh·ªè, m√†u ƒë·ªè ƒë·ªÉ ch·ªâ gi√° tr·ªã l·ªõn c·ªßa h√†m s·ªë.</p>

<p>(M·ªôt m·∫∑t ph·∫≥ng ƒëi qua m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm tr√™n bi√™n c·ªßa m·ªôt t·∫≠p h·ª£p sao cho m·ªçi ƒëi·ªÉm trong t·∫≠p h·ª£p ƒë√≥ n·∫±m v·ªÅ m·ªôt ph√≠a (ho·∫∑c n·∫±m tr√™n) so v·ªõi m·∫∑t ph·∫≥ng ƒë√≥ ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† <em>supporting hyperplane</em> (<em>si√™u ph·∫≥ng h·ªó tr·ª£</em>). N·∫øu m·ªôt t·∫≠p h·ª£p l√† <em>l·ªìi</em>, t·ªìn t·∫°i <em>supporting hyperplane</em> t·∫°i m·ªçi ƒëi·ªÉm tr√™n bi√™n c·ªßa n√≥.)</p>

<p>N·∫øu t·ªìn t·∫°i m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm \(\mathbf{x}_0\) trong <em>feasible set</em> sao cho \(\nabla f_0(\mathbf{x}_0) = 0\), ƒë√¢y ch√≠nh l√† <em>optimal point</em>. ƒêi·ªÅu n√†y d·ªÖ hi·ªÉu v√¨ ƒë√≥ ch√≠nh l√† ƒëi·ªÉm l√†m cho gradient b·∫±ng 0, t·ª©c ƒëi·ªÉm c·ª±c ti·ªÉu c·ªßa h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u. N·∫øu \(\nabla f_0(\mathbf{x}_0) \neq 0\), vector \(-\nabla f_0 (\mathbf{x}_0)\) ch√≠nh l√† <em>vector ph√°p tuy·∫øn</em> c·ªßa <em>supporting hyperplane</em> t·∫°i \(\mathbf{x}_0\).</p>

<p><a name="-gioi-thieu-thu-vien-cvxopt"></a></p>

<h3 id="34-gi·ªõi-thi·ªáu-th∆∞-vi·ªán-cvxopt">3.4. Gi·ªõi thi·ªáu th∆∞ vi·ªán CVXOPT</h3>
<p><a href="http://cvxopt.org/">CVXOPT</a> l√† m·ªôt th∆∞ vi·ªán mi·ªÖn ph√≠ tr√™n Python gi√∫p gi·∫£i r·∫•t nhi·ªÅu c√°c b√†i to√°n trong cu·ªën s√°ch Convex Optimization ·ªü ph·∫ßn T√†i li·ªáu tham kh·∫£o. T√°c gi·∫£ th·ª© hai c·ªßa cu·ªën s√°ch n√†y, Lieven Vandenberghe, ch√≠nh l√† ƒë·ªìng t√°c gi·∫£ c·ªßa th∆∞ vi·ªán n√†y. H∆∞·ªõng d·∫´n c√†i ƒë·∫∑t, t√†i li·ªáu h∆∞·ªõng d·∫´n, v√† c√°c v√≠ d·ª• m·∫´u c·ªßa th∆∞ vi·ªán n√†y c≈©ng c√≥ ƒë·∫ßy ƒë·ªß tr√™n trang web <a href="http://cvxopt.org/">CVXOPT</a>.</p>

<p>Trong ph·∫ßn c√≤n l·∫°i c·ªßa b√†i vi·∫øt, t√¥i s·∫Ω gi·ªõi thi·ªáu 3 b√†i to√°n r·∫•t c∆° b·∫£n trong Convex Optimization: Linear Programming, Quadratic Programming, v√† Geometric Programming. T√¥i c≈©ng s·∫Ω c√πng c√°c b·∫°n l·∫≠p tr√¨nh ƒë·ªÉ gi·∫£i c√°c v√≠ d·ª• ƒë√£ n√™u ·ªü ph·∫ßn ƒë·∫ßu b√†i vi·∫øt d·ª±a tr√™n th∆∞ vi·ªán CVXOPT n√†y.</p>

<p><a name="-linear-programming"></a></p>

<h2 id="4-linear-programming">4. Linear Programming</h2>
<p>Ch√∫ng ta c√πng b·∫Øt ƒë·∫ßu v·ªõi l·ªõp c√°c b√†i to√°n ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n nh·∫•t trong Convex Optimization - Linear Programming (LP, m·ªôt s·ªë t√†i li·ªáu c≈©ng g·ªçi l√† <em>Linear Program</em>), trong ƒë√≥ h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u \(f_0\) v√† h√†m b·∫•t ƒë·∫≥ng th·ª©c r√†ng bu·ªôc \(f_i, i = 1, \dots, m\) ƒë·ªÅu l√† c√°c h√†m tuy·∫øn t√≠nh c·ªông v·ªõi m·ªôt h·∫±ng s·ªë (t·ª©c <a href="/2017/03/19/convexopt/#-linear-programming">h√†m <em>affine</em></a>).</p>

<p><a name="-dang-tong-quat-cua-lp"></a></p>

<h3 id="41-d·∫°ng-t·ªïng-qu√°t-c·ªßa-lp">4.1. D·∫°ng t·ªïng qu√°t c·ªßa LP</h3>
<hr />

<p><strong>A general LP:</strong>
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
\mathbf{x} &amp;=&amp; \arg\min_{\mathbf{x}} \mathbf{c}^T\mathbf{x} + d \<br />
\text{subject to:}~ &amp;&amp; \mathbf{Gx} \preceq \mathbf{h} ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~(19)\<br />
&amp;&amp; \mathbf{Ax} = \mathbf{b}
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>
<hr />

<p>Trong ƒë√≥ \(\mathbf{G} \in \mathbb{R}^{m\times n}, \mathbf{h} \in \mathbb{R}^m\) v√†, \(\mathbf{A}\in \mathbb{R}^{p\times n}, \mathbf{b} \in\mathbb{R}^p\). \(\mathbf{c}, \mathbf{x} \in\mathbb{R}^n\) v√† \(d\) l√† m·ªôt s·ªë v√¥ h∆∞·ªõng (s·ªë v√¥ h∆∞·ªõng n√†y c√≥ th·ªÉ b·ªè qua v√¨ n√≥ kh√¥ng ·∫£nh h∆∞·ªüng t·ªõi nghi·ªám c·ªßa b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u, n√≥ ch·ªâ l√†m thay ƒë·ªïi gi√° tr·ªã c·ªßa h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u). Nh·∫Øc l·∫°i r·∫±ng k√Ω hi·ªáu \(\preceq\) nghƒ©a l√† m·ªói ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ trong vector (ma tr·∫≠n) ·ªü v·∫ø tr√°i nh·ªè h∆°n ho·∫∑c b·∫±ng ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ t∆∞∆°ng ·ª©ng trong vector (ma tr√¢n) ·ªü v·ªÅ ph·∫£i.</p>

<p>Ch√∫ √Ω r·∫±ng nhi·ªÅu b·∫•t ƒë·∫≥ng th·ª©c d·∫°ng \(\mathbf{g}_i\mathbf{x} \leq h_i\), v·ªõi \(\mathbf{g}_i\) l√† c√°c vector h√†ng, c√≥ th·ªÉ vi·∫øt g·ªôp d∆∞·ªõi d·∫°ng \(\mathbf{Gx} \preceq \mathbf{h}\) trong ƒë√≥ m·ªói h√†ng c·ªßa \(\mathbf{G}\) ·ª©ng v·ªõi m·ªôt \(\mathbf{g}_i\), m·ªói ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ c·ªßa \(\mathbf{h}\) t∆∞∆°ng ·ª©ng v·ªõi m·ªôt \(h_i\).</p>

<p><a name="-dang-tieu-chuan-cua-lp"></a></p>

<h3 id="42-d·∫°ng-ti√™u-chu·∫©n-c·ªßa-lp">4.2. D·∫°ng ti√™u chu·∫©n c·ªßa LP</h3>
<p>Trong d·∫°ng ti√™u chu·∫©n (<em>standard form</em>) LP, c√°c b·∫•t ƒë·∫≥ng th·ª©c r√†ng bu·ªôc ch·ªâ l√† ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán c√°c nghi·ªám c√≥ th√†nh ph·∫ßn kh√¥ng √¢m:</p>
<hr />

<p><strong>A standard form LP:</strong>
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
\mathbf{x} &amp;=&amp; \arg\min_{\mathbf{x}} \mathbf{c}^T\mathbf{x} \<br />
\text{subject to:}~ &amp;&amp; \mathbf{Ax} = \mathbf{b} ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~(20)\<br />
&amp;&amp; \mathbf{x} \succeq \mathbf{0}
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>
<hr />

<p>B√†i to√°n \((19)\) c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞a v·ªÅ b√†i to√°n \((20)\) b·∫±ng c√°ch ƒë·∫∑t th√™m bi·∫øn <em>slack</em> \(\mathbf{s}\)</p>
<hr />

<p>\[
\begin{eqnarray}
\mathbf{x} &amp;=&amp; \arg\min_{\mathbf{x}, \mathbf{s}} \mathbf{c}^T\mathbf{x} \<br />
\text{subject to:}~ &amp;&amp; \mathbf{Ax} = \mathbf{b} ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~(21)\<br />
&amp;&amp; \mathbf{Gx} + \mathbf{s} = \mathbf{h} \<br />
&amp;&amp; \mathbf{s} \succeq \mathbf{0}
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>
<hr />

<p>Ti·∫øp theo, n·∫øu ta bi·ªÉu di·ªÖn \(\mathbf{x}\) d∆∞·ªõi d·∫°ng hi·ªáu c·ªßa hai vector m√† th√†nh ph·∫ßn c·ªßa n√≥ ƒë·ªÅu kh√¥ng √¢m, t·ª©c: \(\mathbf{x} = \mathbf{x}^+ - \mathbf{x}^-\), v·ªõi \(\mathbf{x}^+, \mathbf{x}^- \succeq 0\). Ta c√≥ th·ªÉ ti·∫øp t·ª•c vi·∫øt l·∫°i \((21)\) d∆∞·ªõi d·∫°ng:</p>
<hr />

<p>\[
\begin{eqnarray}
\mathbf{x} &amp;=&amp; \arg\min_{\mathbf{x}^+,\mathbf{x}^-, \mathbf{s}} \mathbf{c}^T\mathbf{x}^+ - \mathbf{c}^T\mathbf{x}^- \<br />
\text{subject to:}~ &amp;&amp; \mathbf{Ax}^+ - \mathbf{Ax}^- = \mathbf{b} ~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~(22)\<br />
&amp;&amp; \mathbf{Gx}^+ - \mathbf{Gx}^- + \mathbf{s} = \mathbf{h} \<br />
&amp;&amp; \mathbf{x}^+ \succeq 0, \mathbf{x}^- \succeq 0, \mathbf{s} \succeq \mathbf{0}
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>
<hr />

<p>T·ªõi ƒë√¢y, b·∫°n ƒë·ªçc c√≥ th·ªÉ th·∫•y r·∫±ng \((22)\) c√≥ th·ªÉ vi·∫øt g·ªçn l·∫°i nh∆∞ \((20)\).</p>

<p>B√†i to√°n nh√† xu·∫•t b·∫£n v√† B√†i to√°n canh t√°c trong ph·∫ßn ƒë·∫ßu c·ªßa b√†i vi·∫øt n√†y ch√≠nh l√† c√°c LP.</p>

<p><a name="-minh-hoa-bang-hinh-hoc-cua-bai-toan-lp"></a></p>

<h3 id="43-minh-ho·∫°-b·∫±ng-h√¨nh-h·ªçc-c·ªßa-b√†i-to√°n-lp">4.3. Minh ho·∫° b·∫±ng h√¨nh h·ªçc c·ªßa b√†i to√°n LP</h3>
<p>C√°c b√†i to√°n LP c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c minh ho·∫° nh∆∞ h√¨nh d∆∞·ªõi ƒë√¢y:</p>

<hr />

<div class="imgcap">
 <img src="/assets/17_convexopt/lp.png" align="center" width="600" />
 <div class="thecap">H√¨nh 3. Bi·ªÉu di·ªÖn h√¨nh h·ªçc c·ªßa Linear Programming.</div>
</div>
<hr />

<p>ƒêi·ªÉm \(\mathbf{x}_0\) ch√≠nh l√† ƒëi·ªÉm l√†m cho h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u ƒë·∫°t gi√° tr·ªã nh·ªè nh·∫•t, ƒëi·ªÉm \(\mathbf{x}_1\) ch√≠nh l√† ƒëi·ªÉm l√†m cho h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u ƒë·∫°t gi√° tr·ªã l·ªõn nh·∫•t. V·ªõi c√°c b√†i to√°n LP, nghi·ªám, n·∫øu c√≥, th∆∞·ªùng l√† m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm ·ªü <em>ƒë·ªânh</em> c·ªßa polyheron ho·∫∑c l√† m·ªôt <em>m·∫∑t</em> c·ªßa polyhedron ƒë√≥ (trong tr∆∞·ªùng h·ª£p c√°c ƒë∆∞·ªùng level sets c·ªßa h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u song song v·ªõi m·∫∑t ƒë√≥, v√† tr√™n m·∫∑t ƒë√≥, h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u ƒë·∫°t gi√° tr·ªã t·ªëi ∆∞u).</p>

<p>V·ªÅ LP, c√°c b·∫°n c√≥ th·ªÉ t√¨m th·∫•y r·∫•t nhi·ªÅu t√†i li·ªáu c·∫£ ti·∫øng Vi·ªát (Quy ho·∫°ch tuy·∫øn t√≠nh) v√† ti·∫øng Anh. C√≥ r·∫•t nhi·ªÅu c√°c b√†i to√°n trong th·ª±c t·∫ø c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞a v·ªÅ d·∫°ng LP. Ph∆∞∆°ng ph√°p th∆∞·ªùng ƒë∆∞·ª£c d√πng ƒë·ªÉ gi·∫£i b√†i to√°n n√†y c√≥ t√™n l√† <em>simplex</em> (<em>ƒë∆°n h√¨nh</em>). T√¥i s·∫Ω kh√¥ng ƒë·ªÅ c·∫≠p ƒë·∫øn c√°c ph∆∞∆°ng ph√°p n√†y, thay v√†o ƒë√≥, t√¥i s·∫Ω h∆∞·ªõng d·∫´n c√°c b·∫°n d√πng th∆∞ vi·ªán CVXOPT ƒë·ªÉ gi·∫£i quy·∫øt c√°c b√†i to√°n thu·ªôc d·∫°ng n√†y.</p>

<p><a name="giai-lp-bang-cvxopt"></a></p>

<h3 id="gi·∫£i-lp-b·∫±ng-cvxopt">Gi·∫£i LP b·∫±ng CVXOPT</h3>

<p>T√¥i s·∫Ω d√πng th∆∞ vi·ªán CVPOPT ƒë·ªÉ gi·∫£i B√†i to√°n canh t√°c ·ªü ph√≠a tr√™n. Nh·∫Øc l·∫°i b√†i to√°n canh t√°c:</p>
<hr />

<p><strong>B√†i to√°n canh t√°c:</strong>
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
(x, y) =&amp; \arg\max_{x, y} 5x + 3y \<br />
\text{subject to:}~ &amp; x + y \leq 10 \<br />
                    &amp; 2x + y \leq 16  \<br />
                    &amp; x + 4y \leq 32 \<br />
                    &amp; x, y \geq 0
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>
<hr />

<p>C√°c ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªán r√†ng bu·ªôc c√≥ th·ªÉ vi·∫øt l·∫°i d∆∞·ªõi d·∫°ng \( \mathbf{Gx} \preceq \mathbf{h}\), trong ƒë√≥:</p>

<p>\[
\mathbf{G} = \left[\begin{matrix}
1 &amp; 1 \<br />
2 &amp; 1 \<br />
1 &amp; 4 \<br />
-1 &amp; 0 \<br />
0 &amp; -1
\end{matrix}\right], ~~~~
\mathbf{h} = \left[\begin{matrix}
10\<br />
16 \<br />
32 \<br />
0 \<br />
0
\end{matrix}\right]
\]</p>

<p>L·ªùi gi·∫£i cho b√†i to√°n n√†y khi d√πng CVXOPT l√†:</p>
<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">cvxopt</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">matrix</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">solvers</span>
<span class="n">c</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">matrix</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">5.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">3.</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="n">G</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">matrix</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">2.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">4.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="n">h</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">matrix</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mf">10.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">16.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">32.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">])</span>

<span class="n">solvers</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">options</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'show_progress'</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">False</span>
<span class="n">sol</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">solvers</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">lp</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">c</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">G</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">h</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'Solution"'</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sol</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'x'</span><span class="p">])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Solution:
[ 6.00e+00]
[ 4.00e+00]
</code></pre></div></div>
<p>Nghi·ªám n√†y ch√≠nh l√† nghi·ªám m√† t√¥i ƒë√£ t√¨m ƒë∆∞·ª£c trong ph·∫ßn ƒë·∫ßu c·ªßa b√†i vi·∫øt.</p>

<p>M·ªôt v√†i l∆∞u √Ω:</p>

<ul>
  <li>
    <p>H√†m <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">solvers.lp</code> c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">cvxopt</code> gi·∫£i b√†i to√°n \((21)\).</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>Trong b√†i to√°n c·ªßa ch√∫ng ta, v√¨ ta c·∫ßn t√¨m gi√° tr·ªã l·ªõn nh·∫•t n√™n ta ph·∫£i ƒë·ªïi h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u v·ªÅ d·∫°ng \(-5x - 3y\). Ch√≠nh v√¨ v·∫≠y m√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">c = matrix([-5., -3.])</code>.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>H√†m <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">matrix</code> nh·∫≠n ƒë·∫ßu v√†o l√† m·ªôt <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">list</code> (trong Python), <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">list</code> n√†y th·ªÉ hi·ªán m·ªôt vector c·ªôt. N·∫øu mu·ªën bi·ªÉu di·ªÖn m·ªôt ma tr·∫≠n, ƒë·∫ßu v√†o c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">matrix</code> l√† m·ªôt <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">list</code> c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">list</code>, trong ƒë√≥ m·ªói <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">list</code> b√™n trong th·ªÉ hi·ªán m·ªôt vector c·ªôt c·ªßa ma tr·∫≠n ƒë√≥.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>C√°c h·∫±ng s·ªë trong b√†i to√°n c·∫ßn ·ªü d·∫°ng s·ªë th·ª±c. N·∫øu ch√∫ng l√† c√°c s·ªë nguy√™n, ta c·∫ßn th√™m d·∫•u <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.</code> v√†o sau c√°c s·ªë ƒë√≥ th·ªÉ th·ªÉ hi·ªán ƒë√≥ l√† s·ªë th·ª±c. (T√¥i th·∫•y ƒëi·ªÉm n√†y h∆°i th·ª´a, nh∆∞ng n·∫øu kh√¥ng c√≥ d·∫•u <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">.</code> th√¨ ch∆∞∆°ng tr√¨nh s·∫Ω b√°o l·ªói.)</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>V·ªõi ƒë·∫≥ng th·ª©c r√†ng bu·ªôc \(\mathbf{Ax} = \mathbf{b}\), <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">solvers.lp</code> l·∫•y gi√° tr·ªã m·∫∑c ƒë·ªãnh c·ªßa <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">A</code> v√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">b</code> l√† <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">None</code>, t·ª©c n·∫øu kh√¥ng kh√°i b√°o th√¨ nghƒ©a l√† kh√¥ng c√≥ ƒë·∫≥ng th·ª©c r√†ng bu·ªôc n√†o.</p>
  </li>
  <li>
    <p>V·ªõi c√°c tu·ª≥ ch·ªçn kh√°c, b·∫°n ƒë·ªçc c√≥ th·ªÉ t√¨m trong T√†i li·ªáu c·ªßa CVXOPT.</p>
  </li>
</ul>

<p>Vi·ªác gi·∫£i B√†i to√°n nh√† xu·∫•t b·∫£n b·∫±ng CVXOPT xin nh∆∞·ªùng l·∫°i cho b·∫°n ƒë·ªçc nh∆∞ m·ªôt b√†i t·∫≠p ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n.</p>

<p><a name="-quadratic-programming"></a></p>

<h2 id="5-quadratic-programming">5. Quadratic Programming</h2>
<p><a name="-dinh-nghia-bai-toan-quadratic-programming"></a></p>

<h3 id="51-ƒë·ªãnh-nghƒ©a-b√†i-to√°n-quadratic-programming">5.1. ƒê·ªãnh nghƒ©a b√†i to√°n Quadratic Programming</h3>
<p>M·ªôt d·∫°ng Convex Optimization m√† c√°c b·∫°n s·∫Ω g·∫∑p r·∫•t nhi·ªÅu trong c√°c b√†i sau c·ªßa blog l√† <em>Quadratic Programming</em> (QP, ho·∫∑c <em>Quadratic Program</em>). Kh√°c bi·ªát duy nh·∫•t c·ªßa QP so v·ªõi LP l√† h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u c√≥ d·∫°ng <em>Quadratic form</em>:</p>

<hr />

<p>\[
\begin{eqnarray}
\mathbf{x} &amp;=&amp; \arg\min_{\mathbf{x}} \frac{1}{2} \mathbf{x}^T\mathbf{P}\mathbf{x} + \mathbf{q}^T\mathbf{x} + \mathbf{r} \<br />
\text{subject to:} &amp;&amp;\mathbf{Gx} \preceq \mathbf{h} ~~~~~~~~~~~~~(23)\<br />
&amp;&amp; \mathbf{Ax} = \mathbf{b}
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>
<hr />

<p>Trong ƒë√≥ \(\mathbf{P} \in \mathbb{S}_+^n\) (t·∫≠p c√°c ma tr·∫≠n vu√¥ng n·ª≠a x√°c ƒë·ªãnh d∆∞∆°ng c√≥ s·ªë c·ªôt l√† \(n\)), \(\mathbf{G}\in \mathbb{R}^{m\times n}, \mathbf{A}\in\mathbb{R}^{p \times n}\). <a href="http://machinelearningcoban.com/2017/03/12/convexity/#-quadratic-forms">ƒêi·ªÅu ki·ªán \(\mathbf{P}\) l√† <em>n·ª≠a x√°c ƒë·ªãnh d∆∞∆°ng</em> ƒë·ªÉ ƒë·∫£m b·∫£o h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u l√† <em>convex</em></a>.</p>

<p>Ch√∫ng ta c√≥ th·ªÉ th·∫•y r·∫±ng LP ch√≠nh l√† m·ªôt tr∆∞·ªùng h·ª£p ƒë·∫∑c bi·ªát c·ªßa QP v·ªõi \(\mathbf{P} = \mathbf{0}\).</p>

<p>Di·ªÖn ƒë·∫°t b·∫±ng l·ªùi: trong QP, ch√∫ng ta t·ªëi thi·ªÉu m·ªôt h√†m quadratic l·ªìi tr√™n m·ªôt <em>polyhedron</em>. Xem h√¨nh d∆∞·ªõi ƒë√¢y:</p>
<hr />

<div class="imgcap">
 <img src="/assets/17_convexopt/qp.png" align="center" width="600" />
 <div class="thecap">H√¨nh 4. Bi·ªÉu di·ªÖn h√¨nh h·ªçc c·ªßa Quadratic Programming.</div>
</div>
<hr />

<p><a name="-vi-du-ve-qp"></a></p>

<h3 id="52-v√≠-d·ª•-v·ªÅ-qp">5.2. V√≠ d·ª• v·ªÅ QP</h3>
<p>B√†i to√°n vui: C√≥ m·ªôt h√≤n ƒë·∫£o m√† h√¨nh d·∫°ng c·ªßa n√≥ c√≥ d·∫°ng m·ªôt ƒëa gi√°c l·ªìi. M·ªôt con thuy·ªÅn ·ªü ngo√†i bi·ªÉn th√¨ c·∫ßn ƒëi theo h∆∞·ªõng n√†o ƒë·ªÉ t·ªõi ƒë·∫£o nhanh nh·∫•t, gi·∫£ s·ª≠ r·∫±ng t·ªëc ƒë·ªô c·ªßa s√≥ng v√† gi√≥ b·∫±ng 0.</p>

<!-- (_polyhedron_ - ƒëa gi√°c trong kh√¥ng gian nhi·ªÅu chi·ªÅu, _polyhedra_ - s·ªë nhi·ªÅu c·ªßa _polyhedron_.) -->

<p>B√†i to√°n kho·∫£ng c√°ch t·ª´ m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm t·ªõi m·ªôt polyhedron ƒë∆∞·ª£c ph√°t bi·ªÉu nh∆∞ sau:</p>

<p>Cho m·ªôt polyhedron ƒë∆∞·ª£c bi·ªÉu di·ªÖn b·ªüi \(\mathbf{Ax} \preceq \mathbf{b}\) v√† m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm \(\mathbf{u}\), t√¨m ƒëi·ªÉm \(\mathbf{x}\) thu·ªôc polyhedron ƒë√≥ sao cho kho·∫£ng c√°ch Euclidean gi·ªØa \(\mathbf{x}\) v√† \(\mathbf{u}\) l√† nh·ªè nh·∫•t.</p>

<p>B√†i to√°n n√†y c√≥ th·ªÉ ph√°t bi·ªÉu nh∆∞ sau:
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
\mathbf{x} &amp;=&amp; \arg\min_{\mathbf{x}} \frac{1}{2}||\mathbf{x} - \mathbf{u}||_2^2 \<br />
\text{subject to:} &amp;&amp;\mathbf{Gx} \preceq \mathbf{h}\<br />
\end{eqnarray}
\]
H√†m m·ª•c ti√™u ƒë·∫°t gi√° tr·ªã nh·ªè nh·∫•t b·∫±ng 0 n·∫øu \(\mathbf{u}\) n·∫±m trong polyheron ƒë√≥ v√† <em>optimal point</em> ch√≠nh l√† \(\mathbf{x} = \mathbf{u}\). Khi \(\mathbf{u}\) kh√¥ng n·∫±m trong polyhedron, ta vi·∫øt:
\[
\frac{1}{2} ||\mathbf{x} - \mathbf{u}||_2^2 = \frac{1}{2} (\mathbf{x} - \mathbf{u})^T(\mathbf{x} - \mathbf{u}) = \frac{1}{2} \mathbf{x}^T\mathbf{x} - \mathbf{u}^T\mathbf{x} + \frac{1}{2} \mathbf{u}^T\mathbf{u}
\]</p>

<p>Bi·ªÉu th·ª©c n√†y c√≥ d·∫°ng h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u nh∆∞ trong \((23)\) v·ªõi \(\mathbf{P = I}, \mathbf{q} = - \mathbf{u}, \mathbf{r} = \frac{1}{2} \mathbf{u}^T\mathbf{u}\), trong ƒë√≥ \(\mathbf{I}\) l√† ma tr·∫≠n ƒë∆°n v·ªã.</p>

<p><a name="-vi-du-ve-giai-qp-bang-cvxopt"></a></p>

<h3 id="53-v√≠-d·ª•-v·ªÅ-gi·∫£i-qp-b·∫±ng-cvxopt">5.3. V√≠ d·ª• v·ªÅ gi·∫£i QP b·∫±ng CVXOPT</h3>

<p>X√©t b√†i to√°n sau ƒë√¢y:</p>

<p>\[
\begin{eqnarray}
(x, y) &amp;=&amp; \arg\min_{x, y} (x - 10)^2 + (y - 10)^2 \<br />
\text{subject to:}~&amp;&amp;
\left[\begin{matrix}
1 &amp; 1 \<br />
2 &amp; 1 \<br />
1 &amp; 4 \<br />
-1 &amp; 0 \<br />
0 &amp; -1
\end{matrix}\right]
\left[
\begin{matrix}
x \<br />
y
\end{matrix}
\right]
\preceq
\left[\begin{matrix}
10\<br />
16 \<br />
32 \<br />
0 \<br />
0
\end{matrix}\right]
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>

<hr />

<div class="imgcap">
 <img src="/assets/17_convexopt/qp_ex.png" align="center" width="400" />
 <div class="thecap">H√¨nh 5. V√≠ d·ª• v·ªÅ kho·∫£ng c√°ch gi·ªØa m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm v√† m·ªôt polyhedron.</div>
</div>
<hr />

<p><em>Feasible set</em> trong b√†i to√°n n√†y t√¥i l·∫•y tr·ª±c ti·∫øp t·ª´ B√†i to√°n canh t√°c v√† \(\mathbf{u} = [10, 10]^T\).
B√†i to√°n n√†y c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c gi·∫£i b·∫±ng CVXOPT nh∆∞ sau:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">cvxopt</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">matrix</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">solvers</span>
<span class="n">P</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">matrix</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="n">q</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">matrix</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">10.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">10.</span><span class="p">])</span>
<span class="n">G</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">matrix</span><span class="p">([[</span><span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">2.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">],</span> <span class="p">[</span><span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">4.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="mf">1.</span><span class="p">]])</span>
<span class="n">h</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">matrix</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="mf">10.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">16.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">32.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mf">0.</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">])</span>

<span class="n">solvers</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">options</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'show_progress'</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="bp">False</span>
<span class="n">sol</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">solvers</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">qp</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">P</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">q</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">G</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">h</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'Solution:'</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">sol</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="s">'x'</span><span class="p">])</span>
</code></pre></div></div>
<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>Solution:
[ 5.00e+00]
[ 5.00e+00]
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>Trong c√°c thu·∫≠t to√°n Machine Learning, c√°c b·∫°n s·∫Ω g·∫∑p c√°c b√†i to√°n v·ªÅ t√¨m <em>h√¨nh chi·∫øu</em> (projection) c·ªßa m·ªôt ƒëi·ªÉm l√™n m·ªôt <em>t·∫≠p l·ªìi</em> n√≥i chung r·∫•t nhi·ªÅu. T·ªõi t·ª´ng ph·∫ßn, t√¥i s·∫Ω ƒë·ªÅ c·∫≠p h∆∞·ªõng gi·∫£i quy·∫øt c·ªßa c√°c b√†i to√°n ƒë√≥.</p>

<p><a name="-geometric-programming"></a></p>

<h2 id="6-geometric-programming">6. Geometric Programming</h2>
<p>Trong m·ª•c n√†y, ch√∫ng ta s·∫Ω th·∫•y m·ªôt l·ªõp c√°c b√†i to√°n <em>kh√¥ng l·ªìi</em> khi nh√¨n v√†o h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u v√† c√°c h√†m r√†ng bu·ªôc, nh∆∞ng c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c bi·∫øn ƒë·ªïi v·ªÅ d·∫°ng <em>l·ªìi</em> b·∫±ng m·ªôt v√†i k·ªπ thu·∫≠t.</p>

<p>Tr∆∞·ªõc h·∫øt, ch√∫ng ta c·∫ßn c√≥ m·ªôt v√†i ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a:</p>

<p><a name="-monomials-va-posynomials"></a></p>

<h3 id="61-monomials-v√†-posynomials">6.1. Monomials v√† posynomials</h3>

<p>M·ªôt h√†m s·ªë \(f: \mathbb{R}^n \rightarrow \mathbb{R}\) v·ªõi t·∫≠p x√°c ƒëinh \(\text{dom}f = \mathbf{R}_{++}^n\) (t·∫•t c·∫£ c√°c ph·∫ßn t·ª≠ ƒë·ªÅu l√† s·ªë d∆∞∆°ng) c√≥ d·∫°ng:
\[
f(\mathbf{x}) = c x_1^{a_1} x_2^{a_2} \dots x_n^{a_n}~~~~~~~~(24)
\]
trong ƒë√≥ \(c &gt; 0\) v√† \(a_i \in \mathbb{R}\), ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† m·ªôt <em>monomial function</em> (kh√°i ni·ªám n√†y kh√° gi·ªëng v·ªõi <em>ƒë∆°n th·ª©c</em> khi t√¥i h·ªçc l·ªõp 8, nh∆∞ng khi ƒë√≥ SGK ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a v·ªõi \(c\) b·∫•t k·ª≥ v√† \(a_i\) l√† c√°c s·ªë t·ª± nhi√™n).</p>

<p>T·ªïng c·ªßa c√°c monomials:
\[
f(\mathbf{x}) = \sum_{k=1}^K c_k x_1^{a_{1k}}x_2^{a_{2k}}\dots x_n^{a_{nk}}~~~~~~~~~~(24)
\]
trong ƒë√≥ c√°c \(c_k &gt; 0\) ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† <em>posynomial function</em> (<em>ƒëa th·ª©c</em>), ho·∫∑c ƒë∆°n gi·∫£n l√† <em>posynomial</em>.</p>

<p><a name="-geometric-programming-1"></a></p>

<h3 id="62-geometric-programming">6.2. Geometric Programming</h3>

<p>M·ªôt b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u c√≥ d·∫°ng:</p>

<hr />

<p>\[
\begin{eqnarray}
\mathbf{x}   &amp;=&amp; \arg\min_{\mathbf{x}} f_0(\mathbf{x}) \<br />
\text{subject to:}~ &amp;&amp; f_i(x) \leq 1,  ~~ i = 1, 2, \dots, m ~~~~~~~~~~~(25)\<br />
                    &amp;&amp; h_j(x) = 1, ~~ j = 1, 2, \dots, p
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>
<hr />

<p>trong ƒë√≥ \(f_0, f_1, \dots, f_m\) l√† c√°c <em>posynomials</em> v√† \(h_1, \dots, h_p\) l√† c√°c <em>monomials</em>, ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† <em>Geometric Programming</em> (GP). ƒêi·ªÅu ki·ªán \(\mathbf{x} \succ 0\) ƒë∆∞·ª£c ·∫©n ƒëi.</p>

<p>Ch√∫ √Ω r·∫±ng n·∫øu \(f\) l√† m·ªôt <em>posynomial</em>, \(h\) l√† m·ªôt <em>monomial</em> th√¨ \(f/h\) l√† m·ªôt <em>posynomial</em>.</p>

<p><strong>V√≠ d·ª•:</strong>
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
    (x, y, z)    &amp;=&amp; \arg\min_{x, y, z} x/y                          \<br />
\text{subject to:}~ &amp;&amp; 1 \leq x \leq 2 \<br />
 &amp;&amp; x^3 + 2y/z \leq \sqrt{y} \<br />
 &amp;&amp; x/y = z
\end{eqnarray}
\]
C√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c vi·∫øt l·∫°i d∆∞·ªõi d·∫°ng GP:
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
    (x, y, z)    &amp;=&amp; \arg\min_{x, y, z} xy ^{-1}                        \<br />
\text{subject to:}~ &amp;&amp; x^{-1} \leq 1 \<br />
&amp;&amp; (1/2)x \leq 1 \<br />
&amp;&amp; x^3y^{-1/2} + 2y^{1/2}z^{-1} \leq 1 \<br />
&amp;&amp; xy^{-1}z^{-1} = 1
\end{eqnarray}
\]
B√†i to√°n n√†y r√µ r√†ng l√† <em>nonconvex</em> v√¨ c·∫£ h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u v√† ƒëi·ªÅu ki·ªÉn r√†ng bu·ªôc ƒë·ªÅu kh√¥ng l·ªìi.</p>

<p><a name="-bien-doi-gp-ve-dang-convex"></a></p>

<h3 id="63-bi·∫øn-ƒë·ªïi-gp-v·ªÅ-d·∫°ng-convex">6.3. Bi·∫øn ƒë·ªïi GP v·ªÅ d·∫°ng convex</h3>
<p>GP c√≥ th·ªÉ ƒë∆∞·ª£c bi·∫øn ƒë·ªïi v·ªÅ d·∫°ng l·ªìi nh∆∞ sau:</p>

<p>ƒê·∫∑t \(y_i = \log(x_i)\), t·ª©c \(x_i = \exp({y_i})\). N·∫øu \(f\) l√† m·ªôt <em>monomial function</em> c·ªßa \(\mathbf{x}\) th√¨:
\[
f(\mathbf{x}) = c(\exp({y_1}))^{a_1} \dots (\exp({y_n}))^{a_n} = \exp({\mathbf{a}^T\mathbf{y} + b})
\]
v·ªõi \(b = \log(c)\). L√∫c n√†y, h√†m s·ªë \(g(y) = \exp({\mathbf{a}^T\mathbf{y} + b})\) l√† m·ªôt h√†m l·ªìi theo \(\mathbf{y}\). (B·∫°n ƒë·ªçc c√≥ th·ªÉ ch·ª©ng minh theo ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a r·∫±ng h·ª£p c·ªßa hai h√†m l·ªìi l√† m·ªôt h√†m l·ªìi. Trong tr∆∞·ªùng h·ª£p n√†y, h√†m \(\exp\) v√† h√†m <em>affine</em> tr√™n ƒë·ªÅu l√† c√°c h√†m l·ªìi.)</p>

<p>T∆∞∆°ng t·ª± nh∆∞ th·∫ø, <em>posynomial</em> trong ƒë·∫≥ng th·ª©c \((24)\) c√≥ th·ªÉ vi·∫øt d∆∞·ªõi d·∫°ng:
\[
f(\mathbf{x}) = \sum_{k = 1}^K \exp(\mathbf{a}_k^T\mathbf{y} + b_k)
\]
trong ƒë√≥ \(\mathbf{a}_k = [a_{1k}, \dots, a_{nk}]^T\) v√† \(b_k = \log(c_k)\). L√∫c n√†y, <em>posynomial</em> ƒë√£ ƒë∆∞·ª£c vi·∫øt d∆∞·ªõi d·∫°ng t·ªïng c·ªßa c√°c h√†m \(\exp\) c·ªßa c√°c h√†m <em>affine</em> (v√† v√¨ v·∫≠y l√† m·ªôt h√†m l·ªìi, nh·ªõ l·∫°i r·∫±ng t·ªïng c·ªßa c√°c h√†m l·ªìi l√† m·ªôt h√†m l·ªìi).</p>

<p>B√†i to√°n GP \((25)\) ƒë∆∞·ª£c vi·∫øt l·∫°i d∆∞·ªõi d·∫°ng:
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
    \mathbf{y}    &amp;=&amp; \arg\min_{\mathbf{y}} \sum_{k=1}^{K_0} \exp(\mathbf{a}_{0k}^T\mathbf{y} + b_{0k})                      \<br />
\text{subject to:}~ &amp;&amp; \sum_{k=1}^{K_i} \exp(\mathbf{a}_{ik}^T\mathbf{y} + b_{ik}) \leq 1, ~~, i = 1, \dots, m ~~~~~~(26)\<br />
&amp;&amp; \exp(\mathbf{g}_j^T\mathbf{y} + h_j) = 1, ~ j= 1, \dots, p
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>

<p>v·ªõi \(\mathbf{a}_{ik} \in \mathbb{R}^n, i = 1, \dots, p\) v√† \(\mathbf{g}_i \in \mathbb{R}^n\).</p>

<p>V·ªõi ch√∫ √Ω r·∫±ng h√†m s·ªë \(\log \sum_{i=1}^m \exp(g_i(\mathbf{x}))\) l√† m√¥t h√†m <em>l·ªìi</em> n·∫øu \(g_i\) l√† c√°c h√†m <em>l·ªìi</em> (t√¥i xin b·ªè qua ph·∫ßn ch·ª©ng minh), ta c√≥ th·ªÉ vi·∫øt l·∫°i b√†i to√°n \((26)\) d∆∞·ªõi d·∫°ng <em>l·ªìi</em> b·∫±ng c√°ch l·∫•y \(\log\) c·ªßa c√°c h√†m nh∆∞ sau:</p>
<hr />

<p>GP in convex form:
\[
\begin{eqnarray}
    \text{minimize}_{\mathbf{y}} \tilde{f}_0(\mathbf{y}) &amp;=&amp; \log\left(\sum_{k=1}^{K_0} \exp(\mathbf{a}_{0k}^T \mathbf{y} + b_{i0})\right)                          \<br />
\text{subject to:}~ \tilde{f}_i(\mathbf{y}) &amp;=&amp; \log \left(\sum_{k=1}^{K_i} \exp(\mathbf{a}_{ik}^T \mathbf{y} + b_{ik})\right) \leq 0, ~~ i = 1, \dots, m ~~~~ (27)\<br />
\tilde{h}_j(\mathbf{y}) &amp;=&amp; \mathbf{g}_j^T\mathbf{y} + h_j = 0,~~ j = 1, \dots, p
\end{eqnarray}
\]</p>
<hr />

<p>L√∫c n√†y, ta c√≥ th·ªÉ n√≥i r·∫±ng GP t∆∞∆°ng ƒë∆∞∆°ng v·ªõi m·ªôt b√†i to√°n t·ªëi ∆∞u l·ªìi v√¨ h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u v√† c√°c h√†m b·∫•t ƒë·∫≥ng th·ª©c r√†ng bu·ªôc trong \((27)\) ƒë·ªÅu l√† h√†m l·ªìi, ƒë·ªìng th·ªùi ƒëi·ªÅu hi·ªán ƒë·∫≥ng th·ª©c cu·ªëi c√πng ch√≠nh l√† d·∫°ng <em>affine</em>. D·∫°ng n√†y th∆∞·ªùng ƒë∆∞·ª£c g·ªçi l√† <em>geometric program in convex form</em> (ƒë·ªÉ ph√¢n bi·ªát n√≥ v·ªõi ƒë·ªãnh nghƒ©a c·ªßa GP).</p>

<p><a name="-giai-gp-bang-cvxopt"></a></p>

<h3 id="64-gi·∫£i-gp-b·∫±ng-cvxopt">6.4. Gi·∫£i GP b·∫±ng CVXOPT</h3>
<p>Ch√∫ng ta quay l·∫°i v√≠ d·ª• v·ªÅ B√†i to√°n ƒë√≥ng th√πng <em>kh√¥ng c√≥ r√†ng bu·ªôc</em> v√† h√†m m·ª•c ti√™u l√† \(f(x, y, z) = 40x^{-1}y^{-1}z^{-1} + 2xy + 2yz + 2zx\) l√† m·ªôt posynomial. V·∫≠y ƒë√¢y l√† m·ªôt GP.</p>

<p>Code cho vi·ªác t√¨m <em>optimal point</em> c·ªßa b√†i to√°n n√†y b·∫±ng CVXOPT nh∆∞ sau:</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">from</span> <span class="nn">cvxopt</span> <span class="kn">import</span> <span class="n">matrix</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">solvers</span>
